These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: epic, musical
The people have 2 different jobs:  videographer, fisherman
1. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the videographer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | epic  | musical |
| Job     | fisherman | videographer  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
There 2 different types of food: eggplant, kiwi
There are 2 different nationalities: british, canadian
1. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Food    | eggplant      | kiwi         |
| Nationality   | british | canadian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, soy-milk
The people have 2 different jobs:  project-manager, freelancer
1. the person drinking milk is on the right of the freelancer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | milk   |
| Job       | freelancer  | project-manager |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-4::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: rose, azalea
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, parkour
1. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |
| Flower   | rose  | azalea |
| Sport         | cycling | parkour    |

