.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-7::.
2 different pets are kept: rat, chinchilla
The people have 2 different hobbies: dancing, writing
1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |
| Pet   | rat | chinchilla |
| Hobby      | dancing     | writing  |

